summary: A female Orc I created, where I fought valiantly against \"snarling puke monster\" presets.
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#57a2e5]Pretty Much:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
A female Orc I created, where I fought valiantly against \"snarling puke monster\" presets.

[b][color=#57a2e5]Save File:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
Save file is level 1, right before you make the ULTRA DRAMATIC DECISION whether to follow the Imperial or Stormcloak into the Helgen keep.

[b][color=#57a2e5]Description:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
Pretty much scaled back every possible aggressive / ugly feature of the female Orc. Sorry for leaving her bald, but seriously, in my eyes it was the best looking out of all the hairstyles. And that\'s saying something.

[b][color=#57a2e5]Character Mods Used:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
All of Xenius\' brilliant character detail mods.

[b][color=#57a2e5]Other Saves:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1835]Yet Another Female Nord[/url]
My favourite of the bunch.
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=629]Another Female Nord[/url]
In my mind, pretty much just a draft for the one above.
author: SGommerman
